<h2>InVitness Stopwatch</h2>
<p><span id="seconds">00</span>:<span id="tens">00</span></p>
<button id="button-start">Start</button>
<button id="button-stop">Stop</button>
<button id="button-reset">Reset</button>
</div>

<%# WHen a user hits stop,that should trigger an event listenern which gets the numbers for minutes, seconds and hours and puts them into the form as a param. %>
